      </div>
      <div class="comp-pane comp-pane-preview" data-pane="preview">
        <iframe class="theme-aware" data-base="./sandbox.html?demo=variants-inputs&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="input variants"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-pane comp-pane-code" data-pane="code"><pre><code></code></pre></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── ENHANCERS — interactive ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" id="enhancers">
    <h2>Enhancers — try them live</h2>
    <p class="lead-2">
      The right-hand frame loads the JS bundle. Click headers to sort,
      type in the filter to narrow rows, hit the <code>CSV</code> button
      to download. Same markup is dead-static on the left.
    </p>

    <h3 style="margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight:600">Sortable + filterable table</h3>
    <div class="compare" style="--frame-h: 540px">
      <div class="compare-pane before">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>Before</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=toolbar-table" loading="lazy" title="bare table"></iframe></div>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-pane after">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>After — interactive</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=toolbar-table&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="cms-ui table"></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight:600">Toast notifications</h3>
    <div class="compare" style="--frame-h: 200px">
      <div class="compare-pane before">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>Before</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=toasts" loading="lazy" title="bare toasts"></iframe></div>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-pane after">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>After — click any button</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=toasts&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="cms-ui toasts"></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight:600">Confirm dialog (<code>data-cms-confirm</code>)</h3>
    <div class="compare" style="--frame-h: 220px">
      <div class="compare-pane before">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>Before</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=confirm" loading="lazy" title="bare confirm"></iframe></div>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-pane after">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>After — click "Delete"</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=confirm&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="cms-ui confirm"></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight:600">Command palette (<kbd>Cmd</kbd>+<kbd>K</kbd>)</h3>
    <div class="compare" style="--frame-h: 320px">
      <div class="compare-pane before">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>Before</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=cmdk" loading="lazy" title="bare cmdk"></iframe></div>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-pane after">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>After — focus, then <kbd>Cmd</kbd>+<kbd>K</kbd></div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=cmdk&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="cms-ui cmdk"></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight:600">Inline-edit cells</h3>
    <div class="compare" style="--frame-h: 280px">
      <div class="compare-pane before">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>Before</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=inline-edit" loading="lazy" title="bare inline-edit"></iframe></div>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-pane after">
        <div class="compare-label"><span class="dot"></span>After — click a cell</div>
        <div class="compare-frame-host"><iframe class="theme-aware" src="./sandbox.html?demo=inline-edit&amp;ui=1" loading="lazy" title="cms-ui inline-edit"></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── TOKENS — interactive theming ────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" id="tokens">
    <h2>Theme it in seconds</h2>
    <p class="lead-2">
      Every visual decision in the package is a CSS variable. Override
      one in your app's CSS and every component picks it up — no
      recompile, no fork.
    </p>
    <div id="tokenTester" class="token-tester">
      <div>
        <label>--cms-primary</label>
        <input type="color" name="accent" value="#2563eb">
        <div class="token-value" data-token="accent">#2563eb</div>

        <label style="margin-top:1rem">--cms-radius</label>
        <input type="range" name="radius" min="0" max="20" value="8">
        <div class="token-value" data-token="radius">8px</div>

        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:1rem;line-height:1.5">
          The full token set lives in <code>src/theme/tokens.css</code> —
          spacing, shadows, type, dark-mode overrides.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="token-frame-host">
        <iframe data-base="./sandbox.html?demo=table" title="token preview"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CONFIG ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" id="config">
    <h2>Configure</h2>
    <p class="lead-2">
      Disable any enhancer at runtime via <code>window.cmsUi</code>.
      Disable a single element with <code>data-cms-no-enhance</code>.
    </p>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- Configure before the bundle loads --&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
  window.cmsUi = {
    tables:     { search: true, sort: true, csvExport: false },
    forms:      { tomSelect: true, flatpickr: true, selectThreshold: 8 },
    shortcuts:  true,
    command:    true,
    inlineEdit: false,
    confirm:    true,
  };
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script type="module" src="/static/lib/prism/prism.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre>

    <table class="config-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Key</th><th>Default</th><th>Effect when off</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>tables</code></td><td>on</td><td>No sortable headers, no toolbar.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>forms</code></td><td>on</td><td>Bare <code>&lt;select&gt;</code> / <code>&lt;input type=date&gt;</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>confirm</code></td><td>on</td><td><code>data-cms-confirm</code> ignored.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>loading</code></td><td>on</td><td>No top progress bar.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>toasts</code></td><td>on</td><td><code>cms-toast</code> events ignored.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>shortcuts</code></td><td>on</td><td><code>/</code>, <code>?</code>, <code>g X</code> chords inert.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>command</code></td><td>on</td><td><kbd>Cmd</kbd>+<kbd>K</kbd> palette disabled.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>modalLinks</code></td><td>on</td><td><code>data-cms-modal-link</code> falls back to navigation.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>inlineEdit</code></td><td>on</td><td><code>data-cms-inline-edit</code> cells become static.</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── FEATURES grid ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>What's in the box</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">🎨</span>10+ themed components</h4>
        <p>Tables, forms, buttons, cards, navbar, sidebar, modals, badges, alerts, pagination — all driven by a single token set.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">⌨</span>Keyboard shortcuts</h4>
        <p><kbd>/</kbd> focuses search. <kbd>?</kbd> shows the help overlay. <kbd>Cmd</kbd>+<kbd>K</kbd> opens the command palette. <kbd>g</kbd> chords for navigation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">🔍</span>Sortable, filterable tables</h4>
        <p>Auto-detected on every BS4 striped table. CSV export, column toggle, numeric-column alignment for free.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">ðŸ“…</span>Better selects &amp; datepickers</h4>
        <p>Tom Select replaces big <code>&lt;select&gt;</code>s; Flatpickr replaces <code>&lt;input type="date"&gt;</code>. Both lazy-loaded.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">🌗</span>Dark mode</h4>
        <p>Add <code>data-theme="dark"</code> on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>. Every token has a dark-mode counterpart.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">↔</span>RTL support</h4>
        <p>Add <code>dir="rtl"</code> on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>. Toolbar, sidebar, dropdown, and toast directions flip.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">♿</span>Accessibility-first</h4>
        <p>Focus rings preserved. <code>aria-sort</code> set on sorted headers. <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> honoured. axe-core clean.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">🔌</span>Coexistence</h4>
        <p>Doesn't double-wrap Select2 (.NET runtime), Flatpickr, jQuery UI, or anything tagged <code>data-cms-no-enhance</code>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h4><span class="icon">⚡</span>Tiny &amp; lazy</h4>
        <p>~10 KB gz core JS, ~7 KB gz CSS. Tom Select / Flatpickr only loaded on the first matching element.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── VERIFY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>Verified on both runtimes</h2>
    <p class="lead-2">
      The package ships with a Playwright suite that runs the same tests
      against both runtimes — <code>CaseMaster.Web.exe</code> on
      <code>:5051</code> and <code>cms-vercel</code> on
      <code>:5052</code> — to prove the dual-runtime claim.
    </p>
<pre><code># Boot both runtimes in two terminals, then:
$ npx playwright test
”¦
24 passed (27.0s)

# Visual baselines, axe-core, sortable headers, filter, /, Cmd+K,
# zero console / page errors — verified on both targets.
</code></pre>
  </section>

</main>

<footer>
  <p>
    casemaster-prism · v0.3.0 · MIT.
    <br>
    Source: <a href="/">repository root</a> ·
    Spec: <a href="/AB-ui-package.md">AB-ui-package.md</a> ·
    .NET integration recipe: <a href="/integrations/dotnet/README.md">dotnet/README.md</a> ·
    cms-vercel: <a href="/integrations/vercel/README.md">vercel/README.md</a>
  </p>
</footer>

<script src="/assets/site.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/nav.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
`)
end-function
